law.text:
The court disposition level of the system shall consist of at least the following information as relates to the arraignment:
The court which disposed of the offense;
The name of the judge presiding at the time of disposition;
Date of arraignment;
Listing of each charged offense, and the level thereof, brought before the court at the arraignment;
Listing of the disposition of each charged offense, and the level thereof disposed of by the court at the arraignment; and
Defendant's plea to each offense at the arraignment.
